{"tid":1818884,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"呢個世界唔會有人同你義務抗爭","createTime":"2020-01-10T09:58:37.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-10T15:13:29.000Z","uid":28771,"like":15,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"513d0dddb2ad32c330ded184d187bb2fbe2772f2","tid":1818884,"uid":28771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T09:58:37.000Z","msg":"我想講 非香港人係無義務幫我地抗爭<br />\n佢地肯發聲 應該去感激 <br />\n佢地咁樣已經係做凸左<br />\n<br />\n佢地唔係香港人 唔理香港政治係無可厚非<br />\n到最尾個結果係點 對佢地黎講其實唔會有咩分別<br />\n與其去批鬥D外地既youtuber/KOL無發聲唔表態<br />\n不如去諗下自己有咩可以做 或者有咩做得唔夠<br />\n<br />\n總結: 香港人只需做好份內事 <br />\n唔好為一d對結果無影響既野去浪費精神/時間"},{"pid":"b9c13eb5b4feb6a64b1af37e025980002728e943","tid":1818884,"uid":28771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T10:02:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1fd44185a8d7a1f6f966bf443857466848dab8a","tid":1818884,"uid":127216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T10:09:04.000Z","msg":"推！！！"},{"pid":"8383b90cd2f2621cdb2984f4842bb01da7e13c2c","tid":1818884,"uid":284778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T10:12:37.000Z","msg":"五大訴求 缺一不可！"},{"pid":"2c6e0e5a79c6d4f59fc7eed1ab0b90df4b9bc58a","tid":1818884,"uid":28771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T10:21:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e516b68f8636dafc7929a3e83037dc6d479c105","tid":1818884,"uid":75655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T10:46:13.000Z","msg":"成日都等外國人救<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />,自己付出最少可以得到最大回報<br />\n就好似成日投資想低風險高回報一樣無可能，大把港豬每日都食黃店就當付出左好多，只要唔犯法洗少少錢就當幫左手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，其實我都係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。所以勇武退場係真，大家都毎人比少少錢星火 到最後星火又係比狗搞，所以都係算。"},{"pid":"593ba036b23233f05a5a2599253c4e47a45aaba1","tid":1818884,"uid":28771,"like":0